                    {
                        "name": "Devourer's Dictum",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "The deepmouth warps part of a scalescribed creature's flesh into a mouthed tentacle, then wills it to lash out. The deepmouth makes a jaws Strike that originates from any living scalescribed creature within 120 feet; this Strike also has <a aonid=\"192\" game-obj=\"Traits\">reach 15 feet</a> and deals an additional 2d8 negative damage. If the Strike originates from a creature other than the deepmouth, that creature triggers reactions as though it had made the Strike.",
                        "action": {
